M|Mult|When|
M|Mult|tx|1. **Google Search headlines** (30 chars) — forces the tightest messaging
M|Mult|tx|2. **Expand to Meta headlines** (40 chars) — add a word or two
M|Mult|tx|3. **Expand to LinkedIn intro text** (150 chars) — add context and proof
M|Mult|tx|4. **Expand to Meta primary text** (125+ chars) — full hook and value prop
M|Mult|tx|This cascading approach ensures your core message works everywhere, then gets enriched for platforms that allow more space.